    <description>Leymah Gbowee is a Liberian peace activist and founder of Gbowee Peace Foundation Africa. A 2011 Nobel Peace Prize laureate, she serves on the board of the Nobel Women’s Initiative and is a member of the World Refugee Council.
 
 
